Monday.title: Jiu Jitsu
Monday.subtitle: Morning Crew
Monday.description: A class for all practitioners that have completed fundamentals. Consisting of drills, live drills, and sparring. The class is broken up into 2 parts: Class first followed by sparring. Sparring is optional and not supervised by an instructor.

Monday.title: Conditioning
Monday.subtitle: Strength Training
Monday.description:
A mixture of basic strength training principles and callisthenics performed at a specific work/rest ratio to increase your cardiovascular endurance, power production, and muscle development.
Designed for all levels of fitness as a main source of exercise or as a supplement to your current training program.

Monday.title: Beginner Jiu Jitsu
Monday.subtitle: Advanced Basics
Monday.description: Our beginner program is based off Firas Zahabi's Advanced Basics program. This curriculum was created by one of the worlds most renowned JiuJitsu/MMA coaches to ensure you learn the essential concepts and techniques as a brand new student.

Monday.title: Jiu Jitsu
Monday.subtitle: All Levels
Monday.description: A class for all practitioners that have completed fundamentals. Consisting of drills, live drills, and sparring. The class is broken up into 2 parts: Class first followed by sparring. Sparring is optional and not supervised by an instructor.

Monday.title: MMA
Monday.subtitle: All Levels
Monday.description: Our MMA classes are the perfect mix of striking and grappling. With a heavy emphasis on the basics and strategy, this class is ideal for both beginner and advanced students.
